import React from 'react';
import './App.css';
import { 
  AppBar, 
  Toolbar, 
  Container, 
  IconButton, 
  Typography, 
  Box, 
  Button 
} from '@material-ui/core'
import MenuIcon from '@material-ui/icons/Menu'

function App() {
  return (
    <AppBar position="fixed">
      <Container fixed>
        <Toolbar>
          <IconButton
            color='inherit'
            aria-label='menu'
            edge='start'
          >
            <MenuIcon />
          </IconButton>
          <Typography 
            variant='h6'
          >
            Web Developer Blog
          </Typography>
          <Box>
            <Button
              color='inherit'
              variant='outlined'
            >

            </Button>
          </Box>
        </Toolbar>
      </Container>
      
    </AppBar>  
  );
}

export default App;
